Package: rdtest
Type: Package
Title: Joint Diagnosis for Regression Discontinuity Designs
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
  person("Masayuki","Sawada", email="m-sawada@ier.hit-u.ac.jp",
    role = c("aut","cre")),
  person("Koki","Fusejima",
    role = c("aut")),    
  person("Takuya","Ishihara",
    role = c("aut"))
  )
Description: This package offers a simultaneous implementation of two major 
  diagnostic tests, the density test and balance (placebo) test for regression 
  discontinuity (RD) designs. Running these tests separately result in a serious
  over-rejection of the null hypothesis for justifying a RD design due to 
  multiple testing problem. Our joint test resolve the multiple testing problem.
